  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">The judges for the competition were:<ul><li>Arlene Graham<br></li><li>Marla Winters<br></li><li>Dr. Trent Turner<br></li></ul><span style=\"\"></span><br>The winners in the various categories are as follows...</div>  <div>  <!--BLOG_SUMMARY_END--></div>  <div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"\">Pre-Novice 9 &amp; under</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Trudy Smart<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Priya Bhullar<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Youngest Fiddler</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  Trudy Smart<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Novice 13 &amp; under</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Jaden Howarth<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Jaden Hryniuk<br><span style=\"\"></span>  3. Julie Van Den Bussche<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Junior 18 &amp; under</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Sophie Rivera<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Sylvie Reimer<br><span style=\"\"></span>  3. Stephanie Dousselaere<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Best Old Time Waltz &nbsp;- Under 18 years</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  Stephanie Dousselaere <br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>  <strong style=\"\">Best Reel - Under 18 years</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  Sophie Rivera<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Senior 60 - 70 years</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Bill Gray<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Art Franks<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Golden Agers 71years &amp; up</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Norman Cheyne<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Henri Hince<br><span style=\"\"></span>  3. George Hutlet<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Champion Class</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Alex Lamoureux<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Michael Audette<br><span style=\"\"></span>  3. Jane Cory<br><span style=\"\"></span>  4. Kaitlyn Obedzinski<br><span style=\"\"></span>  5. Russell Hryniuk<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Twin Fiddle Class</strong><br><span style=\"\"></span>  1. Kaitlyn Obedzinski &amp; Jane Cory<br><span style=\"\"></span>  2. Stephanie Reimer &amp; Sylvie Reimer<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Best Old Time Waltz</strong><br>Alex Lamoureux<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Best Reel</strong><br>Michael Audette<br><span style=\"\"></span><br><span style=\"\"></span>    <strong style=\"\">Best Jig</strong><br>Alex Lamoureux<br><span style=\"\"></span></div>  <div><div style=\"height: 20px; overflow: hidden;\"></div> <div id=\"789916988402933018-gallery\" class=\"imageGallery\" style=\"line-height: 0px; padding: 0; margin: 0\"> <div id=\"789916988402933018-imageContainer0\" style=\"float:left;width:49.95%;margin:0;\"><div id=\"789916988402933018-insideImageContainer0\" style=\"position:relative;margin:5px;\"><div class=\"galleryImageBorder\" style=\"border-width:1px;padding:3px;\"><div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;padding:0 0 75%;overflow:hidden;\"><a href=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/3405128_orig.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[gallery789916988402933018]\" onclick=\"if (!window.lightboxLoaded) return false\"><img src=\"/assets/uploads/1/9/6/9/19690537/3405128.jpg\" class=\"galleryImage\" _width=\"333\" _height=\"178\" style=\"position:absolute;border:0;width:140.31%;top:0%;left:-20.15%\"></a></div></div></div></div><div id=\"789916988402933018-imageContainer1\" style=\"float:left;width:49.95%;margin:0;\"><div id=\"789916988402933018-insideImageContainer1\" style=\"position:relative;margin:5px;\"><div 